--------------------------------------------------------------------------
                Development history of Freestyler (Human Resource)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Conventional symbols:

[!] Significant change or extension.
[*] Minor change or extension.
[+] Addition.
[-] Repair of a bug.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------

 4.013 (25-Feb-2001)
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

[*] Changed the colority of some graphic resources. This allowed
    to reduce [fstyler.exe] by 37kB.
[+] Help->Credits item added to the main menu.
[!] Support of Ukrainian. There will be three-language support
    in Freestyler since this version: English, Russian, and Ukrainian.
    Also three-language documentation will be issued.
[*] Before less than 16kB-sized file parts were to be removed with abort 
    of a session. Since now receive resumption is possible from any offset.
[!] Pause on poll (polls). "Hot" keys: Alt+P/Shift+P.
[*] "Hot" keys and behavior of items changed in 'Poll' submenu. 
    E.g. 'Reset' item is non-active when there is nothing to reset.
[!] Since this version Freestyler supports Argus's and older versions of
    Freestyler's configuration files.
         Import of Argus's (of any version) or Freestyler's (up to 4.005) 
    configuration file sets in flags handler (Config->Externals->Flags)
    standard flags, and, also, macros commands, designated to these.
         To import Argus configuration file:
    - copy [config.bin] to Freestyler home directory,
    - remove [fstyler.bin] from there, if exists,
    - start Freestyler.
    If Freestyler misses [fstyler.bin] in its home directory, it will 
    search for [config.bin] to import data. When [fstyler.bin] is
    automatically created, Freestyler will not need [config.bin].
    ATTENTION! Support of Freestyler configuration files is an experiment,
    so, it can work improperly. If you find a bug, mail me, please, 
    information of your Operating System and your version of Freestyler, 
    and do not forget to send me Freestyler configuration file.
    ATTENTION! When upgraded from older versions of Freestyler, do not 
    forget to check settings accuracy in Config->Polls->Options.
    Not needed when upgraded from Argus.
    ATTENTION! Do not apply Freestyler configuration file to Argus.
    (Alexandr Sutulov 2:6083/3.1)
[!] Changed appearance of receive/transfer bars. Added:
    - indicator of file receive/transfer percent;
    - indicator of file receive/transfer elapsed time;
    - indicator of file receive/transfer estimated time;
    - block size indicator;
    - indicators of average (receive and transfer) CPS.
    The same indicators (except for the block size indicator) serve 
    to indicate common receive/transfer process.

