 4.008 (05-Aug-2000)
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
[*] The compiled nodelist can be moved to any folder (not only to
    Freestyler's Home Directory). It is selected in Config->Paths.
[-] Now Freestyler sees Argus's configuration file, except for paths
    configuration.
[*] Renamed the configuration file [config.cfg] => [fstyler.bin].
[-] A minor bug fixed with usage of cursor keys in Outbound window. Now
    'Left'/'Right' keys operate as in standard ListView.
[-] Verification of existence and deletion of [online.Line] flags is 
