 4.005 (15-Jul-2000)
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
[-] The color of the Lamps Bar has been corrected again.
[*] The location of the Settings Folder in the OS registry changed.
    Settings are now located in HKLM\Software\Human Resource\Freestyler.
[*] The main configuration file is renamed [config.bin] => [config.cfg]
    with a view to further modifications of config.
[!] [extcfg.pas] module has been entirely rebuilt.
[!] External flags processing. See them configured in Config->Externals->
    Flags. Flag names must be written in the left column (without paths, 
    as those flags in Freestyler's Home Directory are handled only). 
    If question-mark is put before a flag name then an event occurs on the 
    absence of the flag. The syntax of the right-column lines is the same 
    as in Config->Externals->Cron. A flag is deleted (or created) before 
    command start. There accepted one-minute flags scanning interval. 
    The log-file of external flags processing [flags.log] is located 
    in the Freestyler's Log Directory.
    (Oleg Redut 2:5000/111)
[-] A spelling error corrected ("Nodelist is compling").
    (Vetal Leontev 2:5030/1114)
[-] A spelling error corrected ("Dialling").
    (Alexander Gabalov 2:6053/4.2)
[*] Flag name accuracy check.
[-] Address Input Window overpatched.
    (Gleb Shirenkov 2:5030/518.10)
[+] Folding/unfolding node's Attachment List in 'Outbound' tab using 
    'Left'/'Right' keyboard keys.

